1. API Related Files
API endpoints ➝ src/api/

Ví dụ: userApi.ts

2. Components
Reusable components ➝ src/components/

Structure for each component:

src/components/ComponentName/
├── ComponentName.tsx
├── ComponentName.module.scss
└── ComponentName.types.ts (if needed)
3. Pages
Page components ➝ src/pages/

Structure for each page:

css
src/pages/PageName/
├── PageName.tsx
├── components/
│   └── [PageSpecificComponent].tsx
├── styles/
│   └── PageName.module.scss
└── types/
    └── PageName.types.ts
4. Styles
Global styles ➝ src/styles/

Component styles ➝ ComponentName.module.scss (in respective folder)

Page styles ➝ src/styles/PageName/PageName.module.scss

Use SCSS modules (.module.scss) for scoping

5. Types
Global types ➝ src/types/

Ví dụ: user.types.ts

Component-specific types ➝ ComponentName.types.ts

Page-specific types ➝ src/types/PageName/PageName.types.ts

6. Redux
Reducers ➝ src/redux/reducers/

Ví dụ: userReducer.ts

Actions ➝ src/redux/actions/

Ví dụ: authActions.ts

Selectors ➝ src/redux/selectors/

Ví dụ: productSelectors.ts

Store config ➝ src/redux/store/storeConfig.ts

7. Contexts
Context files ➝ src/contexts/

Structure:

src/contexts/ContextName/
├── ContextNameProvider.tsx
├── ContextName.types.ts
└── ContextName.reducer.ts (if needed)
8. Hooks
Custom hooks ➝ src/hooks/

Ví dụ:

useAuth.ts

usePagination.ts

Group related hooks in subdirectories if needed

9. Constants
Constants ➝ src/constants/

Ví dụ:

appConstants.ts

errorMessages.ts

routes.ts

10. Configurations
App configs ➝ src/configs/

Ví dụ: themeConfig.ts

Environment variables ➝ src/configs/env/

Ví dụ: dev.env.ts

Feature flags ➝ src/configs/features/

Ví dụ: featureToggle.ts

11. i18n
Translation files ➝ src/i18n/locales/

Ví dụ: en.json, vi.json

Language config ➝ src/i18n/config/i18nConfig.ts

i18n utilities ➝ src/i18n/utils/i18nUtils.ts

12. Assets
Images ➝ src/assets/images/

Icons ➝ src/assets/icons/

